    <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://schema.org/safetyConsideration">
        <rdfs:comment>Any potential safety concern associated with the supplement. May include interactions with other drugs and foods, pregnancy, breastfeeding, known adverse reactions, and documented efficacy of the supplement.</rdfs:comment>
